data.Name: Memphis May Fire
data.Bio: Memphis May Fire is an American metalcore band currently based in Dallas, Texas. The band formed in December 2006, but it was not until February 2007 that the group decided on the name Memphis May Fire having previously gone by "O Captain, My Captain!". Since its formation, the band has released two EPs and six full-length albums, the latest being Broken which was released in 2018. Discography: 2007 - Memphis May Fire (EP) 2009 - Sleepwalking 2010 - Between the Lies (EP) Read more on Last.fm
